A cyberpunk cityscape at night where the towering buildings and infrastructure are rendered as semi-transparent structures, revealing intricate glowing circuit boards, flowing data streams, and pulsing code networks running through their cores like a nervous system. The city pulses with neon blues and electric purples, with thin luminous threads connecting every building, vehicle, and streetlight in an invisible web. In the foreground, ordinary people walk past, oblivious to the complex digital architecture humming beneath the surface of their everyday world. Rain-slicked streets reflect the hidden technological heartbeat of civilization, creating a double layer of visible and invisible worlds coexisting.
